prodNameC: 邦迪斯迷你那夫人類免疫球蛋白 G1 套組
ingredientsDesc:
MININEPH IgG1 BUFFER
For use with this lot of IgG1 reagent only. Contains 0.099% Sodium azide as a preservative.
MININEPH HUMAN IgG1 HIGH AND LOW CONTROLS
These consist of pooled normal human serum and are supplied in stabilised liquid form. They contain 0.099% sodium azide, 0.1% EACA and 0.01% benzamidine as preservatives.

MININEPH HUMAN IgG1 ANTISERUM
This has been adsorbed to monospecificity for IgG1 and is supplied in stabilised liquid form. It contains 0.099% sodium azide, 0.1% EACA and 0.01% benzamidine as preservatives.
MININEPH HUMAN IgG1 SWIPE CARD
This is encoded with details of the reaction curve specific to the respective lot of antiserum. This card is antiserum lot specific and must be used only with this lot of antiserum.
